Deenei di mee a mee ne helekai ai i di hai o di buini dauwa o Neco, di king o Egypt, dela ne haga magedaa go Nebuchadnezzar, di king o Babylonia, i Carchemish i taalinga di monowai Euphrates, i di haa ngadau o Jehoiakim nogo king i Judah:46.2 Isaiah 19.1-25; Ezekiel 29.1—32.32
